briefdescription.para: Cereal does not support the serialization of raw pointer.

detaileddescription.para: This macro enable developers to serialize old c-style array by using the above ArrayWrapper class which serialize each member independently.
Omar Shrit Implementation of an array wrapper.
This implementation allows to seriliaze an array easily using cereal.
